        "general_idea": "Upgrade Spring Boot parent version from 2.1.7.RELEASE to 3.2.2 to support JDK 21 and Jakarta EE 9+.",
        "why_exists": "Spring Boot 2.x does not support JDK 21 and uses javax.* packages, causing compilation failures on JDK 21 with Jakarta EE dependencies.",
